	 *                                                    offerorsBankAcount.currency
	 *                                                    (e.g. USD) !=
	 *                                                    commodityCurrency (e.g.
	 *                                                    EURO)
	 * @param amount                                      Money amount
	 * @param pricePerUnit
	 * @param commodityCurrencyOfferorsBankAcountDelegate Delegate to the bank
